{{Top|leg}}
'''Nova-Drive''' was a small manufacturer in the [[Mid Rim/Legends|Mid Rim]] that specialized in license-built starships and built modified versions of ships for niche markets. It sold most of its small range of [[Freighter/Legends|freighters]] in [[Star system/Legends|systems]] along the [[Rimma Trade Route/Legends|Rimma Trade Route]].

One of their major products was the [[3-Z light freighter]], a slightly upgraded [[YT-1200 medium freighter|YT-1200 light freighter]] built under license from [[Corellian Engineering Corporation/Legends|Corellian Engineering Corporation]]. It began making this model a few months after its licensor stopped building them in favor of newer products. Though CEC felt the line had become too old for continued production, Nova-Drive saw a chance to upgrade the design to compete with it in the independent spacer market.

